FBIS4-9345 "dreeu078_b_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-078 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 Bulgaria Prime Minister Berov Released From Hospital Prime Minister Berov Released From Hospital AU2204093794 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 0900 GMT 22 Apr 94 AU2204093794 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Bulgarian BFN [Text] Colonel Dr. Milan Petrov, chief of the Military Medical Academy, informed us a few minutes ago that this morning Prime Minister Lyuben Berov was released from the Lozenets Hospital. It is up to the prime minister whether he will make use of the 15-20 day home rest, which is customary after a cardiovascular operation, or whether he will return immediately to regular activity, of which, according to the medical team, he is sufficiently able, Col. Dr. Milan Petrov said.
